title: Yale Economic Essays
additional-notes: No renewal was filed for the Spring 1964 issue, but it was renewed automatically due to its original 1964 copyright.  A renewal was filed for the next issue, dated Fall 1964.  No other renewals have been explicitly filed.

Some issues of this serial may have distinctive titles.  Before concluding that such an issue is in the public domain, search for book renewals under its distinctive title. We have not systematically searched individual issue titles.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Eli Baum for copyright research on this title.
